### **🚨 AI/ML Quality Standards (ZERO TOLERANCE)**

#### **Model Management**
- **Version Control**: All models must be versioned
- **A/B Testing**: New models require staged rollout
- **Monitoring**: Track accuracy, latency, drift
- **Fallback**: Always maintain CPU-only fallback

#### **Performance Requirements**
- **Inference Latency**: < 10ms for real-time
- **GPU Utilization**: > 80% for batch processing
- **Memory Efficiency**: < 4GB per model
- **Startup Time**: < 30s for model loading

#### **Security & Compliance**
- **Model Isolation**: Each model in separate container
- **Resource Limits**: GPU memory quotas enforced
- **Access Control**: Model API requires authentication
- **Audit Trail**: All predictions logged

